snippet.title: Tank Quest - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1348250/Tank_Quest/

The Tank Lord has taken over the land. Assemble a team or tread solo to defeat his evil forces and take back what is rightfully ours. Take control of a cute animal in a tank and blast through your enemies with your bullets and bombs!
